@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vsvxbi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.42)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.18)) * wp.exp(0.58))
    tmp = 0.49
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs(v0))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs((v0 + 0.74 / tmp + 0.41)))
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.cos(tmp + 0.27) + 0.63))
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.76) / ((v2 + 0.55 + v1 + 0.74) + (v0 + 0.77 - v1 + 0.54)))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.12 * v2 + 0.39) * (v0 + 0.16 + tmp + 0.75)))
    data[tid] = v0
